{
  "stem": "4686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think he went there too many times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was working too hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in that school, there was too many Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Quite a number of Jewish teachers still.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was kept on a-- on a very under level.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're talking-- we're talking early years, we're talking 1938.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- it-- not really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, there was always a couple of big mouths.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But generally, it was frowned upon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we were Hungarians and we stood up and we-- we sing the Himnusz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only difference was that we went to a different class when it came to religious education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, we had a school cap naturally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it had a big I in it, what meant Israel-- Israelite, RG, Realgymnasium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we always said only that this reformatus gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't-- we ignored the I on it because we had to wear the hat, and we didn't want to be too much recognized us as Israelite people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just ignored it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We said can't you see, it's RG, it's reformat gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I would recall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only group I belonged to then was the-- the scout group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a Jewish scout group from the-- from the school, 297 [INAUDIBLE] USF scout group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by that time, Jewish scout group wasn't a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So were behind the cover of our Red Cross group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we did the normal scout things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And instead of the scout symbol, we had a little emblem what just said 297.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till-- till the school was on-- the school, I think, lost somewhere in '44, March, end of March, the school closed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
